    <article class="stage-card" data-accent="amber" id="price">
      <span class="num amber">02 Price</span>
      <h3>Price reliability, toil, and velocity in dollars →</h3>
      <p>Every platform project has expected return, variance, delay cost, blast-radius reduction, and maintenance drag. If you cannot price the queue, you cannot defend the roadmap.</p>
